HEADWORD: Wou-wou
<hw>Wou"-wou`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[So called from its
cry.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The agile, or silvery, gibbon; --
called also camper. See <er>Gibbon</er>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>wow-wow</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

